Package org.gearvrf.scene_objects.view

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GVRView
    Because it is not possible add a Android view to the GVRScene, GVRView is a special view that provides a way to draw View into some GVRViewSceneObject added to the scene graph.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GVRFrameLayout
    This class represents a FrameLayout that is rendered into the attached GVRViewSceneObject.
    GVRTextView
    This class represents a TextView that is rendered into the attached GVRViewSceneObject.
    GVRWebView
    This class represents a WebView that is rendered into the attached GVRViewSceneObject See GVRView and GVRViewSceneObject
